i5.las2peer.classLoaders

Class BundleClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • i5.las2peer.classLoaders.BundleClassLoader

  • public class BundleClassLoader
extends java.lang.ClassLoader
    A BundleClassLoader is responsible of providing all classes for a main class / service via separate libraries.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      BundleClassLoader(java.lang.ClassLoader parent, LibraryClassLoader loader)
      create a simple BundleClassLoader which uses only one library
      BundleClassLoader(java.lang.ClassLoader parent, LibraryClassLoader[] loadersbs)
      create a BundleClassLoader for a bunch of libraries the first library of the given array is the main library of this bundle
      BundleClassLoader(java.lang.ClassLoader parent, LibraryClassLoader mainLoader, java.util.Set<LibraryClassLoader> depLoaders)
      Create a new BundleClassLoader for a set of libraries and a specified main library It does not matter, if the given set of libraries contains the main library.
